#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:5
msgid "Ego Toolbox 的诞生是为了提供更简单、更快速、更纯粹的在线工具体验。"
msgstr ""
"Ego Toolbox was born to provide a simpler, faster and purer online tool "
"experience."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:14
msgid "我们的使命"
msgstr "our mission"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:15
msgid ""
"Ego Toolbox "
"诞生于对“干净、纯粹、高效”工具的渴望。在数字时代，我们每天都需要进行各种数据转换和处理，但网上充斥着大量带有弹窗广告、界面繁杂甚至存在隐私泄露风险的工具。我们希望改变这一现状，为您提供一个现代、极简、即用即走的在线工具平台。"
msgstr ""
"Ego Toolbox was born from the desire for \"clean, pure, and efficient\" "
"tools. In the digital age, we need to perform various data conversion and "
"processing every day, but the Internet is full of tools with pop-up ads, "
"complicated interfaces and even risks of privacy leaks. We want to change "
"that and provide you with a modern, minimalist, out-of-the-box online tool "
"platform."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:19
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "专注体验"
msgid "专注体验，克制设计"
msgstr "Focused Experience"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:20
msgid ""
"我们深受现代产品设计的启发，采用了极其克制的视觉排版和自适应的交互逻辑。无论是 Excel 与 CSV "
"的互转，还是基础的开发工具格式化，我们都将“少即是多”的理念融入每一个像素中，帮助您专注于真正的创作和工作流之中。"
msgstr ""
"We are deeply inspired by modern product design and adopt extremely "
"restrained visual typography and adaptive interaction logic. Whether it's "
"the conversion of Excel and CSV or the formatting of basic development "
"tools, we integrate the concept of \"less is more\" into every pixel to help"
" you focus on real creation and workflow."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:24
msgid "隐私与安全优先"
msgstr "Privacy and security first"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:25
msgid ""
"作为开发者工具团队，我们非常注重数据隐私。Ego Toolbox "
"中的大部分工具均采用纯前端或即时处理后销毁的技术方案。您所上传的任何文件、填写的任何代码和文本，都不会被保存在我们的服务器中。您的数据只属于您自己。"
msgstr ""
"As a developer tools team, we take data privacy very seriously. Most of the "
"tools in Ego Toolbox adopt pure front-end or immediate processing and then "
"destruction technology solutions. Any files you upload, any codes and texts "
"you fill in will not be saved in our server. Your data belongs only to you."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:29
msgid "探索与反馈"
msgstr "Explore and feedback"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/about.html:30
msgid ""
"Ego Toolbox "
"目前仍在快速成长期，我们将持续添加更多开发、办公和生活效率工具。如果您对工具的体验有任何想法，或者希望我们提供某种新工具，欢迎通过顶部的反馈入口联系我们。"
msgstr ""
"Ego Toolbox is still in a period of rapid growth, and we will continue to "
"add more development, office and life productivity tools. If you have any "
"thoughts about your experience with the tool, or if you would like us to "
"provide a new tool, please contact us through the feedback portal at the "
"top."

