#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:4
msgid "CSV与Excel格式对比及最佳适用场景 - Ego Toolbox博客"
msgstr ""
"Comparison between CSV and Excel formats and their best application "
"scenarios - Ego Toolbox Blog"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:5
msgid "深入探讨数据分析与传输中最常见的两种格式：Excel (.xlsx) 和 CSV。为什么我们要在线保留格式互相转换的工具？"
msgstr ""
"A deep dive into two of the most common formats used in data analysis and "
"transfer: Excel (.xlsx) and CSV. Why do we need to keep tools for converting"
" formats online?"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:12
msgid "数据基础科普"
msgstr "Data basic science popularization"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:13
msgid "CSV与Excel格式对比及原理适用场景"
msgstr ""
"Comparison between CSV and Excel formats and application scenarios of the "
"principles"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:17
msgid ""
"在日常办公、财务分析甚至是后端开发的数据交互中，电子表格无疑是最重要的数据载体。然而，很多人往往对 .xls/.xlsx 与 .csv "
"文件之间的核心差异缺乏了解。在这里，我们将对其进行拆解并解释为什么类似于 Ego Toolbox "
"提供的“Excel与CSV互相转换工具”是开发者必备的利器。"
msgstr ""
"In daily office work, financial analysis and even data interaction in back-"
"end development, spreadsheets are undoubtedly the most important data "
"carrier. However, many people often lack understanding of the core "
"differences between .xls/.xlsx and .csv files. Here, we will dismantle it "
"and explain why \"Excel to CSV conversion tool\" similar to that provided by"
" Ego Toolbox is a must-have tool for developers."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:19
msgid "1. 底层原理：富文本结构与纯文本"
msgstr "1. Underlying principles: rich text structure and plain text"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:20
msgid ""
"<strong>Excel 文件（.xlsx）</strong> 本质上是一个包含多个文件、文件夹的压缩包（ZIP 容器）。解压它，您会看到它由一堆 "
"XML 文件组成。正因为这个特性，它可以包含极其丰富的信息：单元格背景色、字体样式、合并单元格信息、复杂的图表，甚至含有可执行的 VBA "
"宏代码。这一切意味着文件尺寸庞大并且解析它需要微软专有或者复杂的第三方库（比如 Apache POI 或 Python 的 `openpyxl`）。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Excel file (.xlsx)</strong> is essentially a compressed package (ZIP"
" container) containing multiple files and folders. Unzip it and you'll see "
"that it consists of a bunch of XML files. Because of this feature, it can "
"contain extremely rich information: cell background color, font style, "
"merged cell information, complex charts, and even executable VBA macro code."
" What this all means is that the file size is huge and parsing it requires "
"Microsoft-proprietary or complex third-party libraries (such as Apache POI "
"or Python's `openpyxl`)."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:21
msgid ""
"<strong>CSV（Comma-Separated Values，逗号分隔值）</strong> "
"则相反。它是一个最为彻底的纯文本文件。所有的行用换行符分开，所有的列用逗号（有时是制表符或分号）隔开。你不仅可以用任何一款轻量级编辑器（如记事本，VSCode）瞬间打开它，世界上几乎所有的编程语言生态都可以用仅仅几行代码完美读取和解析它。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>CSV (Comma-Separated Values)</strong> is the opposite. It is a plain"
" text file at its most thorough. All rows are separated by newlines, and all"
" columns are separated by commas (sometimes tabs or semicolons). Not only "
"can you open it instantly with any lightweight editor (such as Notepad, "
"VSCode), almost all programming language ecosystems in the world can "
"perfectly read and parse it with just a few lines of code."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:23
msgid "2. 我们为什么需要在两者中切换？"
msgstr "2. Why do we need to switch between the two?"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:24
msgid "既然 Excel 如此强大，为什么还要转换给 CSV？答案是<strong>传输效率、机读友好性和跨平台阻抗匹配</strong>。"
msgstr ""
"If Excel is so powerful, why convert to CSV? The answer "
"is<strong>transmission efficiency, machine-readability, and cross-platform "
"impedance matching</strong>."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:26
msgid ""
"<strong>场景 A：大数据导入。</strong> 当你需要将财务提供的 10 万行销售数据导入 MySQL 或 PostgreSQL "
"用户表时，数据库系统本身提供了超高速的 `LOAD DATA INFILE` 或类似 `COPY` 语句。但它们通常仅支持极简的纯文本格式如 CSV。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenario A: Big data import. </strong> When you need to import "
"100,000 rows of sales data provided by finance into a MySQL or PostgreSQL "
"user table, the database system itself provides a super-fast `LOAD DATA "
"INFILE` or similar `COPY` statement. But they usually only support "
"minimalist plain text formats like CSV."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:27
msgid ""
"<strong>场景 B：机器学习训练。</strong> 在 Python 数据科学生态里，`pandas.read_csv()` "
"永远是加载速度最快、消耗内存控制最精准的第一优先级。而直接读取大体积 Excel 会极大拖累性能。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenario B: Machine learning training. </strong> In the Python data "
"science ecosystem, `pandas.read_csv()` is always the first priority with the"
" fastest loading speed and the most accurate memory consumption control. "
"Directly reading large volumes of Excel will greatly drag down performance."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:28
msgid ""
"<strong>场景 C：业务沟通。</strong> "
"当程序员完成数据清洗之后，要交付给运营和财务同事看时，毫无疑问你需要将枯燥的纯文本（或者来自后端的 CSV 报表）转变成带有颜色标记和自动列宽的 "
"Excel 以供汇报。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Scenario C: Business communication. </strong> When your programmers "
"have finished cleaning the data and it's time to hand it over to your "
"operations and finance colleagues, you'll undoubtedly need to turn boring "
"plain text (or a CSV report from the backend) into Excel with color-coding "
"and automatic column widths for reporting."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:31
msgid "3. 工具带来的解决之道"
msgstr "3. Solutions brought by tools"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:32
msgid ""
"许多业务人员发现他们自己打开 CSV 时经常出现“乱码”，核心原因是 Excel 用系统默认的 ANSI 编码（比如 GBK），而生成的 CSV 多为 "
"UTF-8。这也是许多在线转换工具能够通过简单的选项直接解决文字乱码的好处所在。"
msgstr ""
"Many business people find that \"garbled characters\" often appear when they"
" open CSV. The core reason is that Excel uses the system's default ANSI "
"encoding (such as GBK), and the generated CSV is mostly UTF-8. This is also "
"the benefit of many online conversion tools that directly resolve garbled "
"text with simple options."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_csv_vs_excel.html:33
msgid ""
"使用 Ego Toolbox，无论是将包含复杂表头的 Excel 提取出纯粹的二维数据（CSV），还是想要将一团毫无美感的字符（CSV）变成美观的 "
"Excel 输出文件，都只需要一次点击。我们将所有关于编码识别、行尾符解析和 Sheet 工作表剥离的操作隐藏在后台。"
msgstr ""
"Using Ego Toolbox, whether you want to extract pure two-dimensional data "
"(CSV) from Excel containing complex table headers, or you want to turn a "
"bunch of aesthetically pleasing characters (CSV) into a beautiful Excel "
"output file, you only need one click. We hide all encoding recognition, end-"
"of-line character parsing, and sheet stripping behind the scenes."

