#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:13
#: toolbox/views/pages.py:29
msgid "如何利用在线工具提升开发与工作效率"
msgstr "How to use online tools to improve development and work efficiency"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:17
msgid ""
"在这个快节奏的数字时代，程序员和办公人员的日常工作不仅是编写宏大的软件架构或制作精美的演示文稿。更多时候，我们的精力被无数琐碎的小问题所牵扯：如何把这段乱码一样的"
" JSON 数据格式化？怎么把一个几十万行的 Excel 数据给前端作 Mock 使用？怎么快速给张图去个底色？"
msgstr ""
"In this fast-paced digital age, the daily work of programmers and office "
"workers is not just about writing grand software architecture or creating "
"beautiful presentations. More often than not, our energy is involved in "
"countless trivial problems: How to format this garbled JSON data? How to use"
" Excel data with hundreds of thousands of rows for front-end mocking? How to"
" quickly add a background color to a picture?"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:19
msgid "1. 那些消耗你不经意时间的“伪痛点”"
msgstr "1. Those “pseudo pain points” that consume your time unexpectedly"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:20
msgid ""
"之所以称之为“伪痛点”，是因为这些小问题似乎并不需要什么高深的技术。写个 Python 脚本，用 `pandas` 或者原生的 `json` "
"模块，也就是三两分钟的事；或者你可以去搜索引擎搜“JSON 格式化工具”，点开前几个链接，粘贴进去搞定。"
msgstr ""
"The reason why they are called \"pseudo pain points\" is because these small"
" problems do not seem to require any advanced technology. Write a Python "
"script using `pandas` or the native `json` module, which only takes three to"
" two minutes; or you can go to the search engine and search for \"JSON "
"formatting tool\", click on the first few links, and paste it in to get it "
"done."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:21
msgid ""
"然而，细究这背后的心流损失：你需要跳出当前的工作环境，打开新的脚本文件，敲击 Boilerplate "
"代码（模板代码），或者忍受搜索引擎前几个充斥着大量牛皮癣广告和诱导点击的垃圾网站。当你最终获得正确的返回结果时，大脑的工作下文可能已经断片了。"
msgstr ""
"However, look closely at the loss of flow behind this: you need to step out "
"of the current work environment, open a new script file, type Boilerplate "
"code (template code), or endure the first few search engine spam websites "
"filled with a large number of psoriasis ads and induced clicks. By the time "
"you finally get the correct return result, your brain's working context may "
"have been fragmented."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:23
msgid "2. 克制与即用即走（Plug and Play）的哲学"
msgstr "2. The philosophy of restraint and plug-and-play"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:24
msgid "这就是创立 Ego Toolbox 的初衷。一个优秀的工具库应该如同瑞士军刀："
