"This is the original intention of creating Ego Toolbox. A good tool library "
"should be like a Swiss army knife:"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:26
msgid "<strong>它不喧宾夺主：</strong> 没有弹窗提示，没有充值会员按钮，没有闪烁的通知。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>It doesn’t overwhelm the main features:</strong> There are no pop-up"
" prompts, no recharge membership buttons, and no flashing notifications."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:27
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<strong>它单一且专注：</strong> 工具列表清晰。Excel 转 CSV 就只做这个事情。不需要过多的参数选择，预设默认值能满足 90%%"
" 的需求。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>It's single and focused:</strong> The list of tools is clear. Excel "
"to CSV only does this. There is no need for too many parameter selections, "
"and the preset default values ​​can meet 90%% of the needs."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:28
msgid ""
"<strong>它是安全的后盾：</strong> 提供基于浏览器的本地处理，或即时丢弃的内存中转服务，消除您对上传重要内部数据或源码的安全顾虑。"
msgstr ""
"<strong>It's backed by security:</strong> Provides browser-based local "
"processing or instant-discard memory transfer services to eliminate your "
"security concerns about uploading important internal data or source code."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:31
msgid "3. 建立你的桌面工具流标签"
msgstr "3. Create your desktop tool flow tags"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:32
msgid ""
"要想真正提升这些碎片化操作的效率，我们建议您将常用的高频在线工具建立单独的浏览器书签文件夹，或者利用类似 Raycast、Alfred 等启动器为这些 "
"URL 创建快捷方式。当需要验证某段 Base64 字符串时，敲下 `Ctrl + Space`，输入 "
"`b64`，秒进解析网站，转换，复制，关闭。这也是所谓“手指记忆”的终极体现。"
msgstr ""
"To truly improve the efficiency of these fragmented operations, we recommend"
" that you create separate browser bookmark folders for commonly used high-"
"frequency online tools, or use launchers like Raycast, Alfred, etc. to "
"create shortcuts for these URLs. When you need to verify a certain Base64 "
"string, press `Ctrl + Space`, enter `b64`, and the website will be parsed, "
"converted, copied and closed in seconds. This is also the ultimate "
"embodiment of the so-called \"finger memory\"."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:34
msgid "结语"
msgstr "Conclusion"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/blog_improve_efficiency.html:35
msgid ""
"工具是延展人类能力的杠杆，而不应该是消耗心智的累赘。使用干净、高速的 Ego "
"Toolbox，将那些原本必须切分精力的低价值重复处理任务“外包”出去，从而把最锐利的思维，留给真正有挑战性的架构与业务逻辑开发中。期待您在我们的平台上发现属于您的效率之美！"
msgstr ""
"Tools are levers that extend human capabilities, not burdens that consume "
"the mind. Use the clean and high-speed Ego Toolbox to \"outsource\" low-"
"value repetitive processing tasks that must be divided into energy, thereby "
"leaving the sharpest thinking to the truly challenging architecture and "
"business logic development. We look forward to you discovering the beauty of"
" efficiency that belongs to you on our platform!"

