msgstr "In-depth instructions on converting Excel to CSV formats"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:165
msgid "什么是 CSV 格式？"
msgstr "What is the CSV format?"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:166
msgid ""
"CSV（Comma-Separated "
"Values，逗号分隔值）是一种基于纯文本的文件格式。它使用特定的字符（通常是逗号）来分隔数据项，是数据库和电子表格之间进行数据交换的最标准格式之一。与庞大的"
" Excel 文件（如.xlsx）不同，CSV 不包含任何图表、公式或单元格格式，这使得它的数据体积极小，对机器处理和代码读取极其友好。"
msgstr ""
"CSV (Comma-Separated Values) is a plain text-based file format. It uses "
"specific characters (usually commas) to separate data items and is one of "
"the most standard formats for data exchange between databases and "
"spreadsheets. Unlike huge Excel files (such as .xlsx), CSV does not contain "
"any charts, formulas or cell formatting, which makes its data volume "
"extremely small and extremely friendly to machine processing and code "
"reading."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:169
msgid "为什么需要将 Excel 转换为 CSV？"
msgstr "Why do you need to convert Excel to CSV?"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:170
msgid ""
"尽管 Excel 格式在日常人工浏览和排版中具备强大的表现力，但在进行后端开发、数据科学处理及跨系统迁移时，解析庞大的 XML "
"压缩节点往往会引发内存过载。将报表提取为纯文本 CSV，能够使诸如 Python 的 Pandas 库、MySQL "
"的数据导入等操作成倍提升解析效率。这是现代数据工作栈中最基础且必不可少的处理环节。"
msgstr ""
"Although the Excel format is powerful in daily manual browsing and "
"typesetting, parsing huge XML compression nodes often causes memory overload"
" when performing back-end development, data science processing, and cross-"
"system migration. Extracting reports into plain text CSV can double the "
"parsing efficiency of operations such as Python's Pandas library and MySQL's"
" data import. This is the most basic and essential processing step in the "
"modern data work stack."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:173
msgid "Ego Toolbox：极致的安全与隐私保障"
msgstr "Ego Toolbox: Ultimate Security and Privacy Guarantee"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:174
msgid ""
"作为效率工具，我们深知商业与个人数据的敏感性。在使用我们的格式转换功能时，由于采用了轻量级的转换架构，您的表格只会由系统内存即时读取并响应，处理结果下发后即刻从内存中彻底销毁。本站绝不收集、备份或保留任何用户上传的工作表文件。您的数据只属于您自己。"
msgstr ""
"As a productivity tool, we understand the sensitivity of business and "
"personal data. When using our format conversion function, due to the "
"lightweight conversion architecture, your table will only be read and "
"responded to immediately by the system memory, and the processing results "
"will be completely destroyed from the memory immediately after being issued."
" This site never collects, backs up or retains any user-uploaded worksheet "
"files. Your data belongs only to you."

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:177
msgid "如何解决 CSV 文本中常见的字符乱码？"
msgstr "How to solve common character garbled characters in CSV text?"

#: toolbox/templates/toolbox/pages/excel_csv_converter.html:178
msgid ""
"中文乱码通常源于编码不一致——例如业务系统默认导出为 UTF-8 编码，而较早版本的 Excel 则默认使用本地系统的 ANSI "
"编码打开。通过利用我们的『CSV转Excel』工具，底层的自动编码探测器将帮助您抹平编码阻抗，直接输出原生支持解析的正确格式文件，省去您手动添加 "
"UTF-8 BOM 签名的繁琐流程。"
msgstr ""
"Chinese garbled characters usually result from inconsistent encoding - for "
"example, the business system exports to UTF-8 encoding by default, while "
"earlier versions of Excel open using the ANSI encoding of the local system "
"by default. By using our \"CSV to Excel\" tool, the underlying automatic "
"encoding detector will help you smooth out the encoding impedance and "
"directly output the correct format file that natively supports parsing, "
"saving you the tedious process of manually adding UTF-8 BOM signatures."

